      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've tried the specialists. i've tried everything. it just slows the descent, it doesn't stop it. it's like trying to bail out a sinking ship with a spoon. honestly, sometimes i just think about how much more peaceful it would be if it was just... over. if the noise and the pain just stopped forever. it feels like the only real way to get some actual quiet.",
